{"id":"hatach","term":"Hatach","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Verity, one of the eunuchs or chamberlains in the palace of Ahasuerus (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Esther 4:5\">Esther 4:5</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Esther 4:6\">6</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Esther 4:9\">9</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Esther 4:10\">10</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Esther 4:5","Esther 4:6","Esther 4:9","Esther 4:10"]}